main event: A military report documents the sighting of a single white object estimated at second magnitude in the Far East region.
interesting points: The object was sighted at an altitude of 23,530 feet and lost sight at 21,440 feet in clouds,The observation lasted for 2 minutes,The sighting was conducted using binoculars by military personnel,The object was believed to be the Gemini 5 capsule on orbit 94,The report emphasized excellent visibility despite partly cloudy conditions.
sighted object: single white object in the sky
witness description: LT JG Antonino Rossman, USNR and LT JG Thomas Krakker, USN
